posts.title: My thoughts on what's going on 'round here.
posts.content:
These numbers we see here are bad. The top/hot posts are under 1k most of the time, coming from the days of reddit where it was 500k top posts on average, the really big baddies would be 1M plus.

Another thing I see is nothing but bitching. "ELON SUCKS" "MIKE JOHNSON SUCKS" "I SUCK" - where the hell did all the MAGA DRAGON N-R-G go?

I don't like Mike Johnson, either, but can't you all appreciate that Trump is back, despite everything against him, defeating SO MUCH MORE than he ever had to in 2015/2016 era, to get to where he is? And you STILL think he doesn't know what he's doing? He survived BULLETS (not one bullet, not one shooting) when he shouldn't have, he's made it through ALLLLLL THIS SHIT, and we still have these peebly little poindexters nyefnyefnyef sniffing around like little moles finding every fucking thing possible to critique, and this fucking site has no traffic. No users. Fuckin 537 hits is a top post, you shitting me?

Something is off here. I don't know where all those hundreds and thousands of other based posters went, but they ain't here. When I load up a Trump website, I want to feel good, but all I see is bitch bitch bitch.

I'm not saying "I'M LEAVIN'" - this is not one of those posts. However, I can sure as fuck see why so many others have. RULE #1 - BE HERE FOR TRUMP - criticize him some place he'll read it. This is a rally. Be fun and energetic or we end up with lame ass "HOT POSTS" with 537 fucking upvotes as a peak. FFS.

EDIT: I will add this in here since I should have had it to begin with but forgot. Which is sad, because it's the most important part. GOD chose Trump to win, or we wouldn't be standing here like this right now. TRUST GOD if you don't trust Trump and the people he's putting in office. I'm sure he has to support snakes just like he did last time, I just think this time, he knows who they are and will be able to handle them, but not right now, he's not even in office yet.
